<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>XAUUSD AI Scalper | EXNESS + Groq Analysis (Side-by-Side)</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background: #0a0f1a;
            color: #eef2ff;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #111827, #0f172a);
            border-radius: 28px;
            padding: 18px 28px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            border: 1px solid #1e293b;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 16px;
        }
        .title h1 {
            font-size: 1.7rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbbf24, #f59e0b);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }
        .title p {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }
        .status-badge {
            background: #1e293b;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .status-badge.real {
            background: #10b981;
            color: white;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { opacity: 0.6; }
            50% { opacity: 1; }
            100% { opacity: 0.6; }
        }
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
            gap: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .stat-card {
            background: #111827;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #1e293b;
        }
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }
        .stat-value {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-family: monospace;
        }
        .chart-card {
            background: #0f172a;
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            border: 1px solid #1e293b;
        }
        #tradingview-widget {
            width: 100%;
            height: 460px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        /* EXNESS Launch Panel - Enhanced */
        .exness-launch-panel {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2332, #0f172a);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            border: 2px solid #f59e0b;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .exness-info {
            flex: 1;
        }
        .exness-info h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #fbbf24;
        }
        .exness-info p {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }
        .exness-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .btn-exness {
            background: #f59e0b;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #0a0f1a;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
        .btn-exness:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            background: #d97706;
        }
        .btn-exness.secondary {
            background: #334155;
            color: #fbbf24;
        }
        .btn-exness.warning {
            background: #ef4444;
            color: white;
        }
        
        /* Side-by-Side Instructions Card */
        .layout-guide {
            background: #0f172a;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
        }
        .layout-guide h4 {
            color: #3b82f6;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .layout-guide ol {
            margin-left: 20px;
            color: #cbd5e1;
        }
        .layout-guide li {
            margin: 8px 0;
        }
        
        .controls-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .panel {
            background: #111827;
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #1e293b;
        }
        .panel h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        input, select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            background: #0f172a;
            border: 1px solid #334155;
            border-radius: 40px;
            color: white;
            font-family: monospace;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            background: #f59e0b;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-family: inherit;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        button:hover {
            transform: scale(0.98);
            background: #d97706;
        }
        button.success {
            background: #10b981;
            color: white;
        }
        button.danger {
            background: #ef4444;
            color: white;
        }
        button.secondary {
            background: #334155;
            color: #f59e0b;
        }
        button.info {
            background: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
        }
        .flex-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .flex-buttons button {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .signal-box {
            background: #0f172a;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin-top: 16px;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
        }
        .signal {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .signal.BUY { color: #10b981; }
        .signal.SELL { color: #ef4444; }
        .signal.HOLD { color: #fbbf24; }
        .log-area {
            background: #0f172a;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 16px;
            height: 220px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
        }
        .log-entry {
            padding: 6px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #1e293b;
        }
        .api-key-input-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .api-key-input-group input {
            flex: 1;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .api-key-input-group button {
            width: auto;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            background: #3b82f6;
        }
        .quick-trade-card {
            background: #0f172a;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 12px;
            margin-top: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #334155;
        }
        .trade-levels {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 12px;
            margin: 12px 0;
        }
        .level-item {
            background: #00000030;
            padding: 8px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .level-label {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }
        .level-value {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-family: monospace;
        }
        .floating-hint {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            background: #1e293b;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: #fbbf24;
            z-index: 100;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .floating-hint:hover {
            background: #f59e0b;
            color: #0a0f1a;
        }
        @media (max-width: 800px) {
            .controls-row {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .exness-buttons {
                width: 100%;
            }
            .btn-exness {
                flex: 1;
                justify-content: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <div class="title">
            <h1>⚡ XAUUSD AI Scalper + EXNESS Integration</h1>
            <p>REAL Market Data → Groq AI Analysis | Trade on EXNESS (Side-by-Side Window)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="status-badge real">🔴 LIVE REAL DATA</div>
    </div>

    <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-label">XAUUSD (Real Bid)</div><div class="stat-value" id="currentPrice">---</div></div>
        <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-label">Support (24h)</div><div class="stat-value" id="supportVal">---</div></div>
        <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-label">Resistance (24h)</div><div class="stat-value" id="resistanceVal">---</div></div>
        <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-label">RSI (14)</div><div class="stat-value" id="rsiVal">---</div></div>
        <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-label">Data Source</div><div class="stat-value" id="dataSource" style="font-size:0.9rem;">Twelve Data API</div></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Side-by-Side Instructions -->
    <div class="layout-guide">
        <h4><i class="fas fa-desktop"></i> How to use EXNESS side-by-side with this dashboard:</h4>
        <ol>
            <li>Click <strong>"Open EXNESS in New Window"</strong> below - EXNESS will open in a separate browser window</li>
            <li><strong>Resize both windows</strong> to half your screen (Windows: Win+Left/Right Arrow, Mac: Window Tiling)</li>
            <li>Place this dashboard on one half, EXNESS on the other half</li>
            <li>Run AI analysis → Copy trade details → Paste into EXNESS order window</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <!-- EXNESS Launch Panel -->
    <div class="exness-launch-panel">
        <div class="exness-info">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> EXNESS Trading Terminal</h3>
            <p><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Due to EXNESS security policy, iframe embedding is blocked. Opens as separate window for side-by-side trading.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="exness-buttons">
            <button id="openExnessPopupBtn" class="btn-exness">
                <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i> Open EXNESS (XAUUSD)
            </button>
            <button id="openExnessMainBtn" class="btn-exness secondary">
                <i class="fas fa-globe"></i> EXNESS Main
            </button>
            <button id="resizeGuideBtn" class="btn-exness warning">
                <i class="fas fa-window-restore"></i> Split Screen Guide
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="chart-card">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 8px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between;">
            <span><i class="fas fa-chart-simple"></i> XAUUSD Live Chart (TradingView)</span>
            <span class="warning">✅ AI uses REAL market data from Twelve Data API</span>
        </div>
        <div id="tradingview-widget"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="controls-row">
        <div class="panel">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-microchip"></i> Groq AI Analysis</h3>
            <div class="api-key-input-group">
                <input type="password" id="groqApiKey" placeholder="Groq API Key (gsk_...)" value="">
                <button id="saveGroqKey" style="background:#3b82f6;">Save</button>
            </div>
            <div class="api-key-input-group" style="margin-top: 12px;">
                <input type="password" id="twelveDataKey" placeholder="Twelve Data API Key (demo works)" value="demo">
                <button id="saveTwelveKey" style="background:#3b82f6;">Save</button>
            </div>
            <button id="fetchAndAnalyzeBtn" class="success"><i class="fas fa-brain"></i> Fetch REAL Data & Run AI</button>
            <button id="autoAnalyzeBtn" class="secondary"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Auto-Analyze (every 5min)</button>
            <div id="aiOutput" class="signal-box">
                <div style="color:#9ca3af;">⬅️ Enter API keys above, then click "Fetch REAL Data & Run AI"</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-bullhorn"></i> Trade Execution Center</h3>
            <div class="flex-buttons">
                <button id="buyBtn" style="background:#10b981;"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i> BUY XAUUSD</button>
                <button id="sellBtn" style="background:#ef4444;"><i class="fas fa-arrow-down"></i> SELL XAUUSD</button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="quick-trade-card">
                <div class="stat-label" style="text-align: center;">📊 LATEST AI SIGNAL</div>
                <div id="lastSignalDisplay" style="font-weight: 700; font-size:1rem; text-align: center; margin: 8px 0;">—</div>
                <div id="currentTradeLevels" style="display: none;">
                    <div class="trade-levels">
                        <div class="level-item">
                            <div class="level-label">🎯 ENTRY</div>
                            <div class="level-value" id="displayEntry">---</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="level-item">
                            <div class="level-label">📈 TAKE PROFIT</div>
                            <div class="level-value" id="displayTP">---</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="level-item">
                            <div class="level-label">🛑 STOP LOSS</div>
                            <div class="level-value" id="displaySL">---</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="level-item">
                            <div class="level-label">💪 CONFIDENCE</div>
                            <div class="level-value" id="displayConfidence">---</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-buttons" style="margin-top: 8px;">
                    <button id="copyTradeDetails" class="secondary" style="margin-bottom: 0; font-size: 0.8rem;">
                        <i class="fas fa-copy"></i> Copy Details
                    </button>
                    <button id="openExnessQuickBtn" class="info" style="margin-bottom: 0; background: #3b82f6; font-size: 0.8rem;">
                        <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i> Open EXNESS
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <input type="text" id="webhookUrl" placeholder="Webhook URL (optional auto-execution)">
            <button id="manualRefreshPrice" class="secondary"><i class="fas fa-sync-alt"></i> Manual Price Fetch</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="log-area" id="logPanel">
        <div class="log-entry">[System] XAUUSD AI Scalper initialized</div>
        <div class="log-entry">[System] ⚠️ EXNESS blocks iframe embedding for security - opens as separate window</div>
        <div class="log-entry">[System] 💡 Click "Open EXNESS" then use split-screen mode (Windows key + arrow)</div>
        <div class="log-entry">[System] Enter your Groq API key to start AI analysis</div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="floating-hint" id="floatingHint">
    <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> EXNESS opens in new window → Use split screen!
</div>
